metadata.name: OM City Streets: Bear Mode
metadata.description:
What do you do with a bear? Seize the memes of production! Do whatever you can to keep the factory in BUIDL mode, and stay alive. 

This rememe is a remix of SeizeJPGs by 6529er from The Memes by 6529.

Urban street art and CC0 NFTs both embrace a shared mission: art-powered memes, for the culture, gifted to the public. 

I'm fascinated by these intersecting objectives of graffiti and the NFT art CC0 revolution. This series will use photography to explore the themes and give collectors a way to bring more street art into the open metaverse.
